📌 Project Description

The AutoFolio – Vehicle Portfolio Manager is a practical Flutter mobile application designed to help vehicle owners manage their vehicle information, track fuel usage, maintain service records, and monitor expenses.

The application works as a digital vehicle logbook, allowing users to record important vehicle-related data and analyze vehicle performance over time.

This project demonstrates the use of:

Stateful Widgets

Multi-screen Navigation in Flutter

List management and data handling

Form input using TextFormField

Clean UI design using Material Design components

Basic vehicle data tracking and management



---

🚀 Features

✅ Add and manage multiple vehicles
✅ Record fuel entries (litres, cost, odometer reading)
✅ Track vehicle fuel efficiency and mileage
✅ Maintain digital service history records
✅ View recent vehicle activities
✅ Reminder system for maintenance and insurance
✅ Clean dashboard interface with organized vehicle data


