🛠️ Technologies Used

Flutter – Cross-platform mobile development framework

Dart – Programming language used in Flutter

Material Design Widgets – For building responsive UI components

Hive (Local Database) – For offline data storage



---

📱 App Workflow

1️⃣ When the app starts, the user lands on the AutoFolio Dashboard displaying vehicle information and recent activities.

2️⃣ Users can add a new vehicle from the navigation drawer or dashboard.

3️⃣ Users can record fuel entries by entering:

Odometer reading

Fuel litres

Fuel cost


4️⃣ The system tracks fuel data and calculates fuel efficiency and expenses.

5️⃣ Users can open the Service Reminder screen to view upcoming maintenance alerts such as:

Oil change

Insurance renewal

Tyre replacement


6️⃣ The dashboard shows a summary of vehicle data, including mileage and recent activities.


