📂 Project Structure

The project follows a simple Flutter structure with separate screens for different functionalities.

lib/
 ├── main.dart
 ├── screens/
 │    ├── home_page.dart
 │    ├── fuel_entry_screen.dart
 │    └── service_reminder_screen.dart
 ├── models/
 │    └── vehicle.dart

The application uses:

StatefulWidget for dynamic UI updates

Navigator.push() for navigation between screens

TextFormField for user input forms

ListView for displaying records

Local data storage for saving vehicle information



